Package org.apache.poi.hpbf.model.qcbits

Class Summary
QCBit Parent of all Quill CONTENTS bits
QCPLCBit A "PLC " (PLC) based bit of Quill Contents.
QCPLCBit.Type0 Type 0 seem to be somewhat rare.
QCPLCBit.Type12 Type 12 holds hyperlinks, and is very complex.
QCPLCBit.Type4 Type 4 is quite common.
QCPLCBit.Type8 Type 8 is quite common.
QCTextBit A Text based bit of Quill Contents
UnknownQCBit Any Quill Contents bits we don't know how to handle explicitly
